article_id:30,category_name:News,title_name:Concerning Multiplayer Feedback,image_path:,message:<div>We would like to thank everyone who has been playing</div><div>Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><div>Since the game&#39;s release, we have received a lot of player</div><div>feedback concerning multiplayer. In particular, many players</div><div>have found that they run out of getherwings very quickly.</div><div>We are currently investigating how to balance this for</div><div>future events.</div><div><br></div><div>As a thank-you to those who have enjoyed the event</div><div>Loyalty&#39;s Requiem, we would like to offer the following</div><div>items to anyone who started the game by</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539324000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>ãƒ»30 Blessed Ethon Ashes</div><div><br></div><div>You can claim this from your goodies box.</div><div>It must be collected by <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539928799"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1539324000,update_time1539324114